  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with AECOPD and NIV failure and in absence will be treated with NHF device.
      Inclusion criteria are pH &lt; 7,38 and pCO2 &gt; 45 mm Hg. Patients were treated if pH &gt;7,38 or
      refusal of therapy.
    </textblock>
